{"id": "1397359854494027886", "channel_id": "1397359854494027886", "type": 0, "author_id": "885715464775413831", "author_name": "limewareplatter", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello!\nThe description of the items gained for buying 13,000, 16000, 20,000 and 25,0000 silver prime on the spending rewards event \"Gift of Knowledge\" are currently wrong.\n\nAfter the flavor text the tooltip states:\nUse it to obtain 1 random Limited \"`Ultra/Caro/Aequor/Chaos`\" realm `Awakener/WoD`released during \"Faded Legacy\".\n\nThis is not correct. The items allow you to choose an Awakener or Wheel of Destiny, not randomly obtain one.\n\nYou could change it to something like:\nUse it to choose 1 Limited \"`Ultra/Caro/Aequor/Chaos`\" realm `Awakener/WoD`released during \"Faded Legacy\".\n\nThe items affected are the following:\nUltra Mapping: Faded Legacy (13,000 reward)\nUltra Prophecy: Faded Legacy  (13,000 reward)\nCaro Birth: Faded Legacy (16,000 reward)\nCaro Whisper: Faded Legacy (16,000 reward)\nAequor Mystery: Faded Legacy (20,000 reward)\nAequor Codex: Faded Legacy (20,000 reward)\nChaos Echo: Faded Legacy (25,000 Reward)\nChaos Experiment: Faded Legacy (25,000 Reward)\n\nI've attached images of the related items.", "timestamp": "2025-07-22T23:29:11.002000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-22T23:32:16.744000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1397359854812659875", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 197605, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1397359854494027886/1397359854812659875/image.png?ex=6a006c07&is=69ff1a87&hm=8c4b34a0a2c8c9d38da54e9c7be12a7c7b715b5439b4b27a76e8ff65127c5b64&"}, {"id": "1397359855064580137", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 185300, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1397359854494027886/1397359855064580137/image.png?ex=6a006c07&is=69ff1a87&hm=6723351ad1a7b40b0358564a8d980f06b515378f966dfb3c4f66dd9d4b152897&"}, {"id": "139